            <h3>üéØ Goals</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Clarity and Intuition:</strong> Showcase work and capabilities without unnecessary clicks or distractions.</li>
              <li><strong>Performance-First Build:</strong> Ensure fast load times, efficient asset use, and a smooth browsing experience.</li>
              <li><strong>Accessible by Design:</strong> Comply with WCAG standards to make the site usable by all audiences.</li>
              <li><strong>Modern UX Expectations:</strong> Respect users' system-level preferences like dark mode, reduce motion, and high contrast.</li>
              <li><strong>Maintainable and Modular Code:</strong> Build a system that could evolve easily over time.</li>
            </ul>
